In the MATTER OF JONATHAN S., an attorney and counselor-at-law. Attorney Grievance Committee for the First Judicial Department, Respondent,
v.
Jonathan S., Appellant. 2018-696 Court of Appeals of New York. September 6, 2018

***943Motion for reargument and/or clarification of this Court's January 16, 2018 dismissal order dismissed as untimely (see Rules of Ct of Appeals [ 22 NYCRR] § 500.24 [b] ). [see 30 N.Y.3d 1083, 69 N.Y.S.3d 850, 92 N.E.3d 1240 (2018) ]. Motion for renewal of this Court's January 16, ***9442018 dismissal order denied. Motion for a stay dismissed as academic. Motion for other relief denied.
